General.Name: Oscar Properties Holding AB
General.Description: Oscar Properties Holding AB (publ) purchases, develops, manages, and sells real estate properties in Stockholm. Its property portfolio includes warehouses, offices, industrial, grocery retail, and residential units. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
